1
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:14,610
[REBIRTH]

2
00:02:15,070 --> 00:02:17,590
[Episode 22]

3
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,590
Urgent dispatch!

4
00:02:20,710 --> 00:02:22,150
Great victory at Longyin Pass!

5
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,800
Great victory at Longyin Pass!

6
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,520
Qiao won.

7
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,470
Qiao won!

8
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,360
Qiao won!

9
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,400
Look!

10
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:28,520
This is the victory report!

11
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,960
Which one of you
pushed for peace back then?

12
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,360
Aren't you ashamed of yourselves?

13
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,120
Was it you?

14
00:02:33,470 --> 00:02:34,240
Was it you?

15
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:35,270
Your Majesty,

16
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,400
it wasn't me.

17
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:41,280
Qiao has achieved extraordinary merit.

18
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,910
I'll appoint her
as the Left General of Cavalry!

19
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:44,710
Your Majesty,

20
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,960
that is my post.

21
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,820
Then, Right General of Cavalry!

22
00:02:48,820 --> 00:02:50,590
That is General Li Qi's post.

23
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,600
Right, right.

24
00:02:51,670 --> 00:02:53,670
I must think of an even grander title

25
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,840
for her.

26
00:03:11,850 --> 00:03:13,710
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

27
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:20,150
Please rise, both of you.

28
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:26,470
Chu Qiao has defeated Yan Xun

29
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:28,329
and will soon return to Tangjing.

30
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,000
We must act immediately.

31
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:32,590
Otherwise, once Li Ce
consolidates his grip on the throne,

32
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:34,520
it will be hard for us to make a move.

33
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,310
Are your troops ready?

34
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:38,910
They will reach
the outskirts of Tangjing tonight.

35
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,470
With a single order from you,

36
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,120
we will march straight

37
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,400
into the capital!

38
00:03:43,710 --> 00:03:45,120
In recent days, we've been spreading word

39
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,840
of the Xuri Palace incident.

40
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,750
All of Tangjing is buzzing with rumor.

41
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:50,680
The truth
behind Crown Prince Maocheng's death

42
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,150
has come to light,

43
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,710
and the whereabouts of his heir

44
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:55,360
have thrown the city into an uproar.

45
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,220
Your Highness,

46
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:58,600
it's time to reveal your true identity.

47
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:00,610
Your Highness,

48
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,520
I served Crown Prince Maocheng

49
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,630
and have been lying in wait until now.

50
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:05,840
For so many years, we've endured
humiliation and hardship,

51
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,310
waiting for the right moment.

52
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:08,900
Now that moment has come.

53
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,630
We must strike immediately!

54
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:12,400
We must take advantage of the chaos

55
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:15,330
to reclaim
what is rightfully yours, Your Highness.

56
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:27,430
[Tangjing]

57
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,070
Your Majesty is here again,

58
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:58,600
waiting for General Xiuli?

59
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,120
This is the highest spot

60
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,780
in Tangjing, where you can see
all the way north.

61
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,870
If Qiao comes back,

62
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,070
I'll be

63
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,090
the first to spot her from here.

64
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,060
Come on.

65
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,220
Be careful!

66
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:27,680
Thank you.

67
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,240
Ever since General Xiuli came here,

68
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,610
Your Majesty has been fond of her.

69
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,830
Now that she's away on campaign,

70
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:43,159
Your Majesty worries about her every day.

71
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:44,620
If General Xiuli knew,

72
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,720
she would surely be moved
by Your Majesty's devotion.

73
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,310
Her?

74
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,750
No way she would.

75
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:52,140
She only likes fighting and warfare.

76
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:52,920
And I don't want to

77
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,630
tie her down with my feelings.

78
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,390
But

79
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,510
when Qiao comes back,

80
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,120
I'll definitely give her

81
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,070
a grand title—

82
00:06:01,510 --> 00:06:04,290
something even greater
than Sun Di's and Li Qi's combined.

83
00:06:04,290 --> 00:06:05,380
To thank her for

84
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,650
protecting the territory of Biantang
for me.

85
00:06:11,070 --> 00:06:11,680
Li Yan,

86
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,310
you read a lot.

87
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:15,720
Help me see

88
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,300
if the title I've come up with
is any good.

89
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,510
Okay.

90
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:38,360
Why?

91
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,280
I never intended to kill you,

92
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:44,000
but we were destined to end up like this.

93
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,000
What a pity.

94
00:06:49,430 --> 00:06:50,360
You will never get to see

95
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,680
your beloved General Chu return.

96
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,600
Qiao...

97
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,680
I can no longer

98
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,830
protect you...

99
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,700
Your Highness,

100
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:47,000
5,000 imperial guards from nine city gates

101
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,890
of Tangjing

102
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,510
have assembled at the North Gate.

103
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:51,510
A total of 200 gate sentries
have been stationed

104
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,080
at all six gates
on the east and west sides,

105
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,440
awaiting Your Highness's orders.

106
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:54,960
Additionally,

107
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,440
garrison troops from Lingnan and Lingdong

108
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,390
have been deployed 30 li outside Tangjing.

109
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,360
Should anything arise,

110
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:03,420
they can enter the capital immediately
to protect you!

111
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:09,000
-Your subjects,
-Your subjects,

112
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,000
-Xu Su,
-Pei Jian,

113
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,270
respectfully welcome Your Majesty!

114
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:13,390
Long live Your Majesty!

115
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:15,210
We respectfully welcome Your Majesty!

116
00:09:15,210 --> 00:09:16,920
Long live Your Majesty!

117
00:10:11,450 --> 00:10:12,360
Qiao...

118
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:16,270
I can't wait for you anymore.

119
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:28,630
I'm way better

120
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:30,070
than that stone-faced Zhuge Yue.

121
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:33,690
♪ The dust in the world ♪

122
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:32,470
I'm handsome, suave,

123
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:33,800
elegant, and graceful!

124
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,550
I can't spend my whole life
playing the role of

125
00:10:34,210 --> 00:10:37,690
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

126
00:10:36,150 --> 00:10:39,000
a debauched wastrel,
drowning in luxury and carnal indulgence.

127
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:41,190
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

128
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,510
I must first be able to protect myself

129
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:43,320
before I can protect the people
I want to protect.

130
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:43,370
♪ And not be scared? ♪

131
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,410
♪ A slight ripple ♪

132
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:45,600
What does it really feel like

133
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:49,190
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

134
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:47,050
to truly love someone?

135
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,720
To truly love someone

136
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,790
is to feel what they feel.

137
00:10:49,470 --> 00:10:52,840
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

138
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,200
You can sense his happiness,

139
00:10:53,810 --> 00:10:56,650
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

140
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,200
so naturally, you can also feel

141
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,130
the pain and struggle in his heart.

142
00:10:57,320 --> 00:11:00,690
♪ Let it be ♪

143
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,630
You would find joy through him

144
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,820
and naturally feel pain
through him as well.

145
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:13,160
I, by the mandate of Heaven,

146
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,040
reign over all under the sky!

147
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,790
With clear rewards and punishments,

148
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,750
I uphold the moral order of the realm.

149
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:19,270
Now,

150
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:22,240
it has been found that Li Lin,
Minister of Revenue,

151
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:25,200
has embezzled the treasury and engaged in
malpractice for selfish ends.

152
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:28,410
His crimes are beyond dispute,
a flagrant violation of heavenly law.

153
00:11:28,410 --> 00:11:30,050
By law, he is to be executed.

154
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,720
I hereby order the execution
of his entire clan

155
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,870
as a warning to all!

156
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,390
It is noon.

157
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,490
Prepare for the execution!

158
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:45,910
Mother!

159
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:47,670
Execute!

160
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:13,630
Old man,

161
00:12:13,930 --> 00:12:15,990
how long are you going to keep me here?

162
00:12:17,990 --> 00:12:19,800
Not yet.

163
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:23,200
Wait another hour until your son
comes back from the imperial court

164
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:26,240
and tell us how things stand outside.

165
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:27,790
Then I'll decide.

166
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,920
He's just a sixth-rank deputy commander.

167
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:34,600
Why did you let him go to the court?

168
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,120
Not anymore.

169
00:12:36,870 --> 00:12:40,030
I had him resign on your behalf,
citing illness,

170
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,390
and hand over your military tally

171
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:44,390
as a show of loyalty to Li Yan.

172
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:48,480
Li Yan has promoted him
three ranks as a reward.

173
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:52,280
He is now a General.

174
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:56,510
You asked him to hand over
my military command?

175
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:57,940
Who gives you the right
to make decisions for me?

176
00:12:57,940 --> 00:12:58,580
Sun Di!

177
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,930
You're my daughter's husband.

178
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,600
What you do affects not only yourself

179
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,790
but also the lives of

180
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:08,450
my daughter and my whole clan!

181
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:12,170
At a time like this,

182
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,620
never mind military command—

183
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,050
as long as we can keep our lives,

184
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,840
even if you have to play the fool,

185
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,310
you must keep playing along!

186
00:13:20,310 --> 00:13:22,960
Li Yan is nothing but a treasonous rebel
who usurped the throne!

187
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,060
I'll lead my troops

188
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,550
into the palace and kill him right now!

189
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,350
And then what?

190
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:28,760
The late emperor is dead.

191
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,400
Who will take the throne?

192
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:33,980
Who will take charge of
the overall situation in Biantang?

193
00:13:42,050 --> 00:13:43,110
Or do you...

194
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,500
want to become the next Li Yan?

195
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,200
Close the door

196
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,050
and add a few more locks.

197
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,510
No one is allowed in or out.

198
00:14:01,290 --> 00:14:04,200
Let this fool cool his head.

199
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:17,310
The imperial edict of investiture
has been issued.

200
00:14:17,310 --> 00:14:18,790
You are now Empress.

201
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,040
Your Majesty,

202
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:22,000
why do you put yourself through this?

203
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,200
Ask them all to leave.

204
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:25,170
Your Majesty...

205
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,840
His Majesty has arrived!

206
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:36,320
Leave.

207
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:48,840
Chun'er,

208
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:50,350
what's wrong?

209
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:56,350
I've been on the throne for over a month.

210
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,240
Yet you still refuse to

211
00:15:01,370 --> 00:15:02,830
wear the empress's robes.

212
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:05,550
And you've declined to accompany me

213
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:07,820
to every state banquet and ceremony.

214
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,720
What exactly are you unhappy about?

215
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:15,700
You're now the most honored woman
in all the world.

216
00:15:15,770 --> 00:15:17,510
All the pain you've endured before

217
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:18,790
is in the past.

218
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,350
What more do you want?

219
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:21,700
Or is it that...

220
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:24,650
I have not treated you well?

221
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:26,240
Li Yan.

222
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:29,880
Who exactly are you?

223
00:15:35,730 --> 00:15:36,890
When I first met you,

224
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:41,530
you said you were just a scion
of a noble family in Biantang.

225
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:43,870
But when I came to Tangjing with you,

226
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,180
I found out you were the Prince of Luo.

227
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,630
I believed you,

228
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,750
thinking you were marginalized
outside the imperial court

229
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:51,960
and humiliated,

230
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,360
so I wanted to help you
reclaim a little of

231
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:55,820
the dignity
a royal descendant should have.

232
00:15:58,630 --> 00:16:00,120
But then you transformed

233
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:02,240
into who you are now.

234
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,840
It's not that I refuse to be your empress.

235
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,080
I'm just bewildered—

236
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:09,030
who are you, really?

237
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:11,790
It feels as though I've never
truly known you.

238
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:13,120
Will there come a day

239
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:15,180
when I stand atop the walls

240
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,920
of Tangjing
in my empress's ceremonial robes,

241
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,840
only to die

242
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:21,820
in your arms the very next moment?

243
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:25,670
Zhao Chun'er,

244
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:27,030
you think you are the only one

245
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:29,160
who has suffered grievances and pain?

246
00:16:30,910 --> 00:16:32,270
If you don't want to

247
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,490
wear the empress's attire,

248
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:38,360
I won't force you.

249
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:45,240
Biantang is in chaos right now.

250
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:49,120
Just stay in the palace and rest well.

251
00:17:01,170 --> 00:17:02,280
[Ministry of War Office]

252
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:01,440
Why are you here?

253
00:18:01,550 --> 00:18:02,750
How is General Xiuli?

254
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,550
My situation is
a bit complicated right now.

255
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:05,270
Lord Sun.

256
00:18:06,190 --> 00:18:06,800
You know

257
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:08,730
what this is, right?

258
00:18:11,600 --> 00:18:12,640
Minister Xu!

259
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,110
Minister Xu!

260
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:15,160
Bad news!

261
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:16,480
Sun Di...

262
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,010
Sun Di has mobilized troops
from the Southeastern Guard Camp,

263
00:18:18,010 --> 00:18:20,070
50 li east of the city, into the palace!

264
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:21,350
He may be plotting rebellion!

265
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:22,070
Sun Di?

266
00:18:22,590 --> 00:18:23,720
The military tally is in my hands.

267
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,830
How did he mobilize anyone?

268
00:18:24,830 --> 00:18:26,720
Go assemble
the imperial guards immediately.

269
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,160
I'll go to the palace
to protect the Emperor myself.

270
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:28,510
Yes, sir!

271
00:18:28,510 --> 00:18:29,240
Minister Xu!

272
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:30,960
The Ministry of War has just sent word

273
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,350
that someone broke into the office
last night,

274
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,350
and the military tally
of the Southeastern Guards is missing!

275
00:18:34,350 --> 00:18:35,160
Come with me!

276
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,070
You told me once

277
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:09,360
that in this deep palace,

278
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:12,000
power and the throne

279
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,440
matter far more than blood ties.

280
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:16,480
At first, I didn't understand.

281
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:20,090
I even blamed you
for not wanting to acknowledge me.

282
00:19:20,090 --> 00:19:21,330
I'll take my leave.

283
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:22,880
But now I understand.

284
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,440
And I've done it—

285
00:19:24,970 --> 00:19:27,140
even better than you, Mother.

286
00:19:28,030 --> 00:19:30,290
And I understand it more deeply than you.

287
00:19:55,250 --> 00:19:55,900
Mother,

288
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,090
if you were still alive

289
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,280
and could see who I am today,

290
00:20:00,990 --> 00:20:02,320
you would probably be

291
00:20:03,310 --> 00:20:04,480
proud of me.

292
00:21:58,880 --> 00:21:59,960
I knew

293
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:02,060
Xu Su's men couldn't kill you.

294
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,480
I knew you would come back for me.

295
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:06,400
You knew I'd come to kill you

296
00:22:06,830 --> 00:22:07,790
for Li Ce?

297
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:09,000
I knew.

298
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,830
But I'm not afraid.

299
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:12,850
Because this is my fate.

300
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:15,240
Li Ce was not your enemy.

301
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:17,400
Why couldn't you let him go?

302
00:22:17,550 --> 00:22:18,950
From the very beginning,

303
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:22,880
it was always one or the other—
Li Ce or me.

304
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:24,720
If I hadn't killed him,

305
00:22:25,110 --> 00:22:27,770
one day he would've discovered
my true identity

306
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:29,950
and moved to eliminate me all the same.

307
00:22:29,950 --> 00:22:31,320
He wouldn't.

308
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:43,510
Move aside!

309
00:22:44,070 --> 00:22:46,360
I need to enter the palace
to see His Majesty!

310
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:47,120
Lord Xu,

311
00:22:47,790 --> 00:22:50,430
I've received His Majesty's order
to protect him.

312
00:22:50,430 --> 00:22:52,490
No one is allowed to enter the palace.

313
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:54,550
Go back.

314
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:55,310
Sun Di,

315
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:58,490
you're no longer
the Left General of Cavalry.

316
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:01,350
Your son resigned on your behalf
two days ago,

317
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:02,920
and His Majesty approved it!

318
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:05,070
Otherwise, do you think
you and your family

319
00:23:05,070 --> 00:23:07,400
could still live peacefully in Biantang?

320
00:23:09,190 --> 00:23:10,720
The military tally is here.

321
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:14,160
I'm acting on His Majesty's verbal decree.

322
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:16,350
There are rebels among the imperial guards
in the capital.

323
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:19,480
I was ordered to mobilize troops
from the Southeast Camp

324
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,590
into the capital
to protect the Imperial City.

325
00:23:21,590 --> 00:23:24,370
By His Majesty's order, none may enter
without imperial authorization.

326
00:23:24,370 --> 00:23:25,500
How dare you, Sun Di!

327
00:23:25,550 --> 00:23:26,790
You broke into the Ministry of War Office

328
00:23:26,790 --> 00:23:28,480
and stole the military tally
of the Southeastern Guards!

329
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:30,440
This is a capital crime that warrants
the execution of your entire clan!

330
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:32,570
Lord Xu, you must be talking nonsense.

331
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:36,790
His Majesty handed the military tally
to me personally.

332
00:23:36,790 --> 00:23:38,310
You must have forgotten.

333
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:41,070
All soldiers, listen to my command!

334
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:42,730
You're Biantang's soldiers!

335
00:23:42,790 --> 00:23:44,110
I'm the Minister of War!

336
00:23:44,110 --> 00:23:46,160
The criminal Sun Di
has stolen the military tally

337
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,160
and committed treason!

338
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,640
Seize him immediately!

339
00:23:51,590 --> 00:23:52,830
The military tally is here!

340
00:23:52,830 --> 00:23:54,360
I am the General of Cavalry!

341
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:55,930
Who dares move?

342
00:23:58,310 --> 00:23:59,160
Li Ce

343
00:23:59,550 --> 00:24:02,880
was never worthy of this dragon robe
from the day he was born!

344
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:19,480
General Chu,

345
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:23,030
this is a family matter
between Li Ce and me.

346
00:24:23,030 --> 00:24:24,830
You didn't have to get involved.

347
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:26,590
Li Ce helped you,

348
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:29,000
but he also did it to use you.

349
00:24:29,230 --> 00:24:30,630
If you hadn't helped him,

350
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:33,440
he wouldn't have sat on that throne
for even a single day.

351
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,770
If you hadn't saved him,

352
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:37,870
he might have been killed
by my mother long ago.

353
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,110
Yes.

354
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:42,830
She was also his mother.

355
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:44,960
Come to think of it,

356
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:48,510
we were true brothers by blood.

357
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,750
Did you not help Li Ce

358
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:01,440
simply to rebuild your Xiuli Army?

359
00:25:01,990 --> 00:25:04,120
You and Li Ce were allies, true enough,

360
00:25:04,590 --> 00:25:06,590
but I can give you all of that too.

361
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:44,880
In the royal family,

362
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:47,830
even blood ties mean nothing—

363
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:51,440
let alone the meager friendship
between you two.

364
00:25:51,750 --> 00:25:52,680
How can

365
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:56,010
friendship be more reliable
than interests?

366
00:25:56,240 --> 00:25:57,200
What do you want?

367
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:58,710
General Xiuli?

368
00:25:59,110 --> 00:26:00,070
Prince of Xiuli?

369
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,510
Or Queen Xiuli?

370
00:26:02,750 --> 00:26:04,350
An assassin is in the palace!

371
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:06,170
Soldiers, heed my command—

372
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:08,660
enter the palace to protect His Majesty!

373
00:26:22,070 --> 00:26:23,160
General Chu,

374
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:26,880
we can make a deal.

375
00:27:05,270 --> 00:27:05,880
Li Yan,

376
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:07,740
Li Ce was not

377
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:09,830
a bargaining chip for power.

378
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,790
He was my friend.

379
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,960
The new Emperor Li Yan is dead.

380
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:21,160
There is no need to protect him.

381
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:22,920
Chu Qiao has assassinated the Emperor!

382
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,350
Her crime is unforgivable!

383
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:26,550
Kill Chu Qiao immediately!

384
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,820
Xu Su, guilty of treason and regicide,

385
00:28:54,820 --> 00:28:56,350
has already been executed!

386
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:57,750
Soldiers, hear my command!

387
00:28:57,750 --> 00:29:00,750
Seize all of his personal guards!

388
00:29:01,820 --> 00:29:04,020
Imperial guards who acted unknowingly

389
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:06,110
under Xu Su's orders—

390
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:07,830
surrender,

391
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:10,560
and you will be pardoned!

392
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:26,450
♪ The dust in the world ♪

393
00:29:26,970 --> 00:29:30,440
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

394
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:31,680
Qiao is the world-renowned General Chu.

395
00:29:31,150 --> 00:29:33,950
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

396
00:29:32,150 --> 00:29:34,830
"General Chu Meets
the Crown Prince of Biantang By Chance—

397
00:29:34,780 --> 00:29:36,130
♪ And not be scared? ♪

398
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:38,310
Fake Drama Turns Into Real Fate."

399
00:29:36,150 --> 00:29:38,170
♪ A slight ripple ♪

400
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:41,940
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

401
00:29:42,220 --> 00:29:45,590
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

402
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:44,960
Qiao...

403
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:49,410
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

404
00:29:50,070 --> 00:29:53,440
♪ Let it be ♪

405
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:57,950
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

406
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:57,270
Qiao,

407
00:29:57,920 --> 00:30:00,030
I'm giving
these 3,000 imperial guards to you.

408
00:29:58,430 --> 00:30:01,440
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

409
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:02,510
They shall guard you just as they

410
00:30:01,820 --> 00:30:03,450
♪ Go weaving ♪

411
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:03,880
protect me.

412
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:08,730
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

413
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,310
Li Ce,

414
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:08,240
I haven't fulfilled my promise to you yet.

415
00:30:09,250 --> 00:30:12,050
♪ We once beheld ♪

416
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:15,480
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

417
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:19,840
♪ Beauty never ♪

418
00:30:19,860 --> 00:30:24,590
♪ Lasts for long ♪

419
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:23,760
[Mihe Abode]

420
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:28,380
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

421
00:30:28,410 --> 00:30:32,840
♪ It's just a stone ♪

422
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:40,350
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

423
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:39,750
Xing.

424
00:30:42,270 --> 00:30:43,750
I want to avenge Li Ce.

425
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:45,600
I must kill the Prince of Luo!

426
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:46,640
Xing,

427
00:30:47,110 --> 00:30:48,370
Li Yan is already dead.

428
00:30:48,700 --> 00:30:50,630
You killed him with your own hands.

429
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:52,310
No!

430
00:31:01,750 --> 00:31:02,310
Xing.

431
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:06,680
Everything is over now.

432
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:09,550
Li Ce has been avenged.

433
00:31:11,110 --> 00:31:12,240
It's all in the past.

434
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:18,830
It's all over now?

435
00:31:28,070 --> 00:31:29,110
You've done

436
00:31:30,110 --> 00:31:31,370
everything you could.

437
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:33,440
And you did it well.

438
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:40,960
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

439
00:31:41,080 --> 00:31:43,620
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

440
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:42,830
You can

441
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:45,360
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

442
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:45,510
leave it all behind now.

443
00:31:45,380 --> 00:31:46,840
♪ My longing surges ♪

444
00:31:46,870 --> 00:31:49,380
♪ I become haggard ♪

445
00:31:49,990 --> 00:31:52,430
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

446
00:31:52,470 --> 00:31:55,290
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

447
00:31:55,310 --> 00:31:57,010
♪ My love remains ♪

448
00:31:57,320 --> 00:32:00,690
♪ But you're already gone ♪

449
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:02,990
♪ What I seek in life ♪

450
00:32:03,010 --> 00:32:04,600
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

451
00:32:04,620 --> 00:32:07,210
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

452
00:32:07,230 --> 00:32:08,820
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

453
00:32:08,840 --> 00:32:12,030
♪ My longing still rests ♪

454
00:32:12,050 --> 00:32:14,410
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

455
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,950
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

456
00:32:15,980 --> 00:32:18,630
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

457
00:32:18,650 --> 00:32:23,510
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

458
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:24,940
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

459
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:27,210
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

460
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:29,680
♪ How do we start over? ♪

461
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:33,010
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

462
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:35,290
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

463
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:38,730
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

464
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:41,070
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

465
00:32:41,090 --> 00:32:43,970
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

466
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:48,540
♪ In the end ♪

467
00:32:50,170 --> 00:32:54,380
♪ It can only be praised ♪

468
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,400
A weak ruler over a strong state

469
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:20,880
is an omen of instability for the nation!

470
00:33:21,070 --> 00:33:23,440
General Xiuli, Chu Qiao,
is hereby conferred

471
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,700
the title of Imperial Consort Xiuli!

472
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:26,190
I'll leave the 500 guards

473
00:33:26,850 --> 00:33:28,160
Li Ce promised me to you.

474
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,920
Where have you gone now?

475
00:33:30,110 --> 00:33:30,720
Miss!

476
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,430
I have a favor to ask of you.

477
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:34,200
No matter how the royal clan schemes

478
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,720
or how chaotic the world becomes,

479
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:37,690
nothing shall ever separate us again.

480
00:33:37,690 --> 00:33:38,350
Don't come over.

481
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:39,030
Don't come over!

